
  Sceptile    Grass Type Pokémon

  The leaves growing on SCEPTILE’s 
  body are very sharp edged.  This 
  Pokémon is very agile - it leaps 
  all over the branches of trees 
  and jumps on its foe from above 
  or behind. 
	   Evolution Chain
